commit.message:
[AArch64] Removed unused SLOWMUL target flags

	* config/aarch64/aarch64.h (AARCH64_TUNE_SLOWMUL): Delete.
	(AARCH64_FL_SLOWMUL): Delete.
	(AARCH64_FL_CRC): Redefine to 1<<3.
	(AARCH64_FL_USE_FMA_STEERING_PASS): Redefine to 1<<4.
